 ## most common CSS properties: 

| **Category**       | **Property**          | **Description**               | **Example**                |
|---------------------|-----------------------|--------------------------------|-----------------------------|
| **Text & Font**    | `color`              | Changes text color            | `color: blue;`             |
|                   | `font-family`        | Sets the font type            | `font-family: Arial;`      |
|                   | `font-size`          | Controls text size            | `font-size: 16px;`         |
|                   | `font-weight`        | Adjusts text boldness         | `font-weight: bold;`       |
|                   | `font-style`         | Sets font style (italic, etc.)| `font-style: italic;`      |
|                   | `text-align`         | Aligns text horizontally      | `text-align: center;`      |
|                   | `text-decoration`    | Adds text decorations         | `text-decoration: underline;` |
|                   | `text-transform`     | Changes capitalization        | `text-transform: uppercase;` |
|                   | `letter-spacing`     | Adjusts space between letters | `letter-spacing: 2px;`     |
|                   | `line-height`        | Adjusts space between lines   | `line-height: 1.5;`        |
| **Layout & Box Model** | `width`          | Sets element width            | `width: 100%;`            |
|                   | `height`             | Sets element height           | `height: 200px;`          |
|                   | `margin`             | Outer space around element    | `margin: 10px;`           |
|                   | `padding`            | Inner space inside element    | `padding: 15px;`          |
|                   | `border`             | Adds a border                 | `border: 1px solid black;` |
|                   | `display`            | Defines display behavior      | `display: flex;`          |
|                   | `position`           | Defines positioning           | `position: relative;`     |
|                   | `overflow`           | Manages content overflow      | `overflow: hidden;`       |
| **Background Styling** | `background-color` | Sets background color         | `background-color: #f0f0f0;` |
|                   | `background-image`   | Adds background image         | `background-image: url('bg.jpg');` |
|                   | `background-size`    | Resizes background image      | `background-size: cover;` |
|                   | `background-repeat`  | Sets background repeat        | `background-repeat: no-repeat;` |
| **Flexbox**       | `display: flex`      | Enables flexbox layout        | `display: flex;`          |
|                   | `justify-content`    | Aligns content horizontally   | `justify-content: space-between;` |
|                   | `align-items`        | Aligns content vertically     | `align-items: center;`    |
|                   | `flex-wrap`          | Controls item wrapping        | `flex-wrap: wrap;`        |
| **Grid**          | `display: grid`      | Enables grid layout           | `display: grid;`          |
|                   | `grid-template-columns` | Defines column structure   | `grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;` |
|                   | `grid-template-rows` | Defines row structure        | `grid-template-rows: 100px auto;` |
|                   | `gap`                | Adds spacing between items    | `gap: 10px;`              |
| **Pseudo-classes** | `:hover`            | Applies style on hover        | `a:hover { color: red; }` |
|                   | `:focus`             | Applies style on focus        | `input:focus { border: 2px solid blue; }` |
| **Pseudo-elements** | `::before`         | Inserts content before        | `p::before { content: 'Note: '; }` |
|                   | `::after`            | Inserts content after         | `p::after { content: ' End'; }` |
| **Responsive Design** | `@media`         | Styles for specific devices   | `@media (max-width: 600px) {}` |
|                   | `vw`, `vh`           | Viewport width/height units   | `width: 50vw;`            |
| **Units of Measurement** | `px`          | Absolute unit (pixels)        | `font-size: 16px;`        |
|                   | `%`                 | Percentage                    | `width: 50%;`            |
|                   | `em`                | Relative to parent font size  | `font-size: 2em;`        |
|                   | `rem`               | Relative to root font size    | `font-size: 1.5rem;`     |
| **Advanced CSS**  | `z-index`           | Controls stacking order       | `z-index: 10;`           |
|                   | `opacity`           | Sets transparency level       | `opacity: 0.5;`          |
|                   | `transition`        | Adds smooth animation         | `transition: all 0.3s ease;` |
|                   | `transform`         | Applies transformations       | `transform: rotate(45deg);` |
|                   | `box-shadow`        | Adds shadow to elements       | `box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px gray;` |

---

This table highlights the **key CSS properties** across different areas, making it easy to understand and reference when designing or developing web pages.
